---
title: Orchestrator Pull Pattern — workflow reads upstream observations, passes as activity input
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator<br/>(Temporal Workflow)
    participant TEMPORAL as Temporal
    participant REDIS as Redis Streams
    participant BS as blindspot-detector<br/>(Temporal Worker)

    Note over ORC,BS: Precondition: coverage-left, coverage-center,<br/>coverage-right, source-validator STOP messages received.

    Note over ORC,REDIS: Orchestrator reads cross-agent data from Redis Streams<br/>and passes it as input to the activity.<br/>No direct agent-to-agent connection exists.

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:claim-4821-run-003:coverage-left - +<br/>filter: code matches COVERAGE_*
    REDIS-->>ORC: observations [COVERAGE_ARTICLE_COUNT,<br/>COVERAGE_FRAMING, COVERAGE_TOP_SOURCE]

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:claim-4821-run-003:coverage-center - +
    REDIS-->>ORC: observations

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:claim-4821-run-003:coverage-right - +
    REDIS-->>ORC: observations

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:claim-4821-run-003:source-validator - +
    REDIS-->>ORC: observations [SOURCE_EXTRACTED_URL,<br/>SOURCE_VALIDATION_STATUS, SOURCE_CONVERGENCE_SCORE, CITATION_LIST]

    ORC->>ORC: consolidate upstream observations<br/>into activity input payload

    ORC->>TEMPORAL: schedule activity: blindspot-detector<br/>({<br/>  run_id: "claim-4821-run-003",<br/>  task: "analyze_blindspot",<br/>  upstream_observations: [<br/>    {agent: "coverage-left", obs: [...]},<br/>    {agent: "coverage-center", obs: [...]},<br/>    {agent: "coverage-right", obs: [...]},<br/>    {agent: "source-validator", obs: [...]}<br/>  ]<br/>})

    TEMPORAL->>BS: execute activity with upstream data

    Note over BS: Agent reasons over consolidated<br/>coverage data. Publishes observations<br/>to its own stream.

    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=synthesis

    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_SCORE, 0.78, P)<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_DIRECTION, RIGHT, P)

    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_SCORE, 0.12, F)<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_DIRECTION, NONE, F)<br/>publish(CROSS_SPECTRUM_CORROBORATION, FALSE, F)

    BS->>REDIS: XADD progress:claim-4821-run-003 *<br/>agent=blindspot-detector event=observations_published
    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F

    BS-->>TEMPORAL: activity complete ({<br/>  agent: "blindspot-detector",<br/>  status: "COMPLETE",<br/>  observationCount: 5<br/>})

    TEMPORAL-->>ORC: activity result

    ORC->>REDIS: XREADGROUP — consume STOP
    ORC->>ORC: mark blindspot-detector COMPLETE
